caption.rendered:
HDR shot of an arcade in Paris, “La Galerie Vivienne”, built in 1823.

There are about a dozen of really beautiful arcades like this one in Paris, and each is different in something. I really like the ambiance in this particular one.

And, one more thing : the christmas tree is not photoshopped, it was really red like this 😉

Lens: Sigma 18-200
